reviewText: Cute  little  movie. In  some  spots  it  gets  a  bit  chessy  but  over all i  liked  it.  You're  going  to  want  to  give  the neighbor a  good  smack
A brilliant film that shows a delicate subject with a lovely outcome.

I have to say I really liked it!  The plot was well developed except that the neighbor lady should have gotten what she deserved.  This is kind of a musical as there are some musical scenes in it.  I loved Amina's Papa in particular.  It does have English subtitles for those who are wondering.
